Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:20.53,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.16,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,He stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.16,0:00:29.29,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,He stopped the \Ncalamity 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's what he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.98,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,but he doesn't seem to \Nremember any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.98,0:00:39.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Reiko, do you remember \NMr. Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:42.91,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Of course. We were \Nin the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.70,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:50.14,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Did he ever... \Nsay how he stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:55.32,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I don't remember \Nhearing anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:01:00.04,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You went on a class trip during summer that year, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:01.19,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:06.32,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,We didn't think it was \Na good idea to stay{ confined at} home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.37,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What happened on that trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.83,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'm sure something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:15.61,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,but I can't seem to remember what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:17.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.89,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Sorry. I know I'm no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.14,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:28.62,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm fine. You don't \Nneed to go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:33.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Matsunaga \Nwent on the trip too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:36.44,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.50,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:41.14,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Was he acting strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.99,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:48.32,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I guess our only \Noption is to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:53.22,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,All right. I'll run it \Nby Matsu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:56.11,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'll tag along when \Nyou go talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.64,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.14,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.06,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:09.82,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's with all that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:12.29,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I stocked up on supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.07,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:25.87,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,Are you okay? \NYou don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.06,Default,Nakao,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm just a bit carsic—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.25,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,He's a tough one. {lit. He tries too hard.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:37.85,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You're coming as well, Akazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.58,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:42.30,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Why don't you ride in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.29,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yours doesn't look like \Nit can fit four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:46.91,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,This car runs better \Nthan you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.31,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,That was unnecessary. {alt. You don't need to say that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.89,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.90,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,All right, Teshigawara. \NYou're riding with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.02,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.10,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Nakao, you're sitting in the \Nfront since you get carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.03,Default,Nakao,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:17.46,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.59,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Matsunaga won't be \Nreturning to Yomiyama for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.25,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I spoke with his mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.72,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,and she said he's living at the resort hotel where he works.
