Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:04.84,Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(-105.3,133.4)\fscx1652.6\fscy1633.1\bord0\shad0\c&H283439&\3c&H929EA3&\an5\fs5\fsp0.39\fnCronos Pro Light\b1\clip(m 111 83 b 115 125 155 250 154 309 l 581 313 463 25)}Please Come Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.42,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,We safely made it \Nout of Yomiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.65,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.94,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,All right, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.29,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.45,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.54,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Uh, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.34,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Sheesh. If you're going to drive that slow, then get out of the fast lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:47.93,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I guess you can't judge \Na book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I think you're pretty easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.63,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.74,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Describe me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:56.77,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Eh? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Strong and dependable, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:02.48,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You think I'm that macho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Well, you're tough, and you've \Ngot a strong sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.01,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:10.74,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You should at least say, \N"That's not what I meant."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.70,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.91,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,What the hell? You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.99,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I've gotta get back \Nat you every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:26.70,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You're the head \Nof countermeasures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,How do you get picked for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.51,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,It's usually chosen by the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.06,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,It's not a very popular job. {alt. No one really wants to do it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:38.16,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You could say that they're responsible for the lives of everyone in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.64,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So, you were appointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.61,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I nominated myself. {alt. I volunteered./I rose to the task. (I don't think it's common to say "I nominate myself" in this case)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:48.02,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Perhaps nobody else \Nbelieved in the calamity,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.71,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,but I was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:54.64,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I can't let a senseless \Nphenomenon exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.50,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going \Nto put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.05,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,It's hot as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.48,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Matsunaga was called to \Na reception, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.56,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I left my cell number with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:27.41,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,so he should call \Nwhen he gets back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.17,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What should we do until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.61,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,No point sittin' around \Ndoing nothing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:34.36,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. We came all \Nthis way, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:38.41,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,We're outside of Yomiyama, \Nso the calamity shouldn't affect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:40.73,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Right! Let's go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.44,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,We {\i1}are{\i0\fsp4} {\r}near the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.40,Default,All,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.11,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I don't have my swimsuit \Nwith me, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.74,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,You can get some \Nat the hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.21,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,They're not expensive. \NI'll even buy you a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.18,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,But... I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,If you're not going \Nto swim, then I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.95,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Well, I thought this \Nmight happen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.91,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Eh? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I knew you guys \Nbrought too much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.55,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Well, we {\i1}are{\i0\fsp4} {\r}near the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.00,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Not to mention we're \Noutside of Yomiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.65,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,It's also summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.21,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,It'd be depressing to sit inside all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.68,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,We need to have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.01,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.59,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,The summer ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.43,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.02,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.36,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.48,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Sakakibara...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.22,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,My glasses! I can't see \Nwithout my glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.40,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.58,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Ready, and... dunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:49.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, is your family's \Nsummer house nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.77,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What does your dad do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm not too sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.62,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's rarely ever in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:03.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That's why, on the occasions he's actually \Nhome, we put on these little family facades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:08.37,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,We might be family, but it \Ndoesn't feel like we're related.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.71,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:15.73,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, if we found out who \Nthe dead person is after this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:19.72,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,would making them \Nnonexistent stop the calamity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:22.79,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I don't think that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:24.96,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's already been triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.99,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I think it's too late \Nto try balancing it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,They connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's not so bad to connect \Nevery now and then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.75,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.42,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Anyone up for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.43,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.05,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.79,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Should we go back to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.64,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm fine with going \Nto a convenience store. {OR eating from one}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.97,Default,Sugiura,0,0,0,,There are shops along the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.61,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Hold it, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.61,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,We're at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.19,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,We should make the most \Nout of an outdoor life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.53,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You want to cook here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.16,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,All right, Akazawa! \NI knew you'd understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.22,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.37,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,How do you expect us \Nto cook without any tools? {OR tools}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.44,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I've got it covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.37,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes on \Nthis flawless setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.45,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:39.30,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So this is what you were carrying? {in that bag}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.05,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Are you going to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.92,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.37,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,With what ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.55,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Duh! We'll get that locally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:48.87,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.68,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,With all the stuff you \Nbrought, I should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.53,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Locally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:57.45,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Mochizuki! You brought \Nthe fishing gear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.36,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:03.09,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,All right. Let's see who can \Ngather the most ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What are the prizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.21,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Whoever loses has to cook the food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.08,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,and whoever wins gets to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.12,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.04,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.39,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,It's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.40,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,All right. I'll pick the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.27,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,First off, on the Head of \NCountermeasures Team will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.38,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:22.38,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sugiura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.72,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Naka— Actually, never mind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.10,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.96,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Now, on the Nonexistent Team will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:30.03,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.89,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.85,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Mochizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.68,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,But I exist—!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.53,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you don't \Nexist over {\i1}here{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.69,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,That's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.93,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So we're competing based on the number of fish we catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:45.57,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,No. If you find \Nanything else, it counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.82,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's sea lettuce. It tastes awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,That's red algae. \NYou can't eat it by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.01,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.64,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,It's a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.50,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.19,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,It's kelp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.12,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You're supposed to catch {\i1}fish{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.50,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.27,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.64,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Get it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I thought it was going to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Octopuses don't eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.79,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,They'll bite if you \Npoke at them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.05,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.37,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I think I've got a big one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.65,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,It's pulling pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.86,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.46,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,That's your big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.02,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,At least it's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.84,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.16,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I've got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.19,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.23,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You're doing this \Non purpose, aren't yo—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.23,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.26,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,A sea cucumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.65,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm impressed \Nthat you even caught one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.48,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Maybe it just got caught on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.66,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,You creep! Useless jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:58.66,Alternative,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:02.29,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,A blowfish, an octopus, \Nand a starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.25,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,This is kelp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.34,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,And a sea cucumber, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.04,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,What's in this shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.88,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,A hermit crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.31,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I guess that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:19.26,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,The battle ends with a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.10,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I picked up some \Nmeat and vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.98,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,so let's cook that. {OR eat that}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.22,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.24,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Fresh seafood is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.31,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,The crunch is so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,We can't eat these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.64,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:10.52,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.51,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I tried calling your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.03,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Is your battery dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:16.02,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.27,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.59,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Careless as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.37,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you found us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.20,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,It wasn't hard to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:28.63,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,This is the closest \Nbeach to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.66,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.75,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,But wow,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:33.99,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,girls sure do change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.92,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,You used to be such a shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.07,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,You've changed a bit, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.48,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,You're an old geezer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.51,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Oh, shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.43,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,It's been 15 years, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.95,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Technically, it's only been \N14 years since our graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.02,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:56.22,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,That makes us around 30, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.99,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Shut it. {alt. Don't remind me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.37,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.39,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Haven't I seen you \Naround recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.67,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.62,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I don't remember seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.87,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,It was probably someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.82,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I don't think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:14.71,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Maybe at Kentarou or \NNatsuko's memorial service?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:18.60,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,No, I only went to their funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.70,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.35,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's been \N15 years since they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.45,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Who're the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:29.51,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,This year's class 3 students.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.30,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.11,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,They're here to find out about what happened 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:39.82,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can only remember bits and pieces about that summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.28,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Matsu, I heard that you \Nstopped the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:48.04,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Tomoka over at Inoya \Nasked me the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.60,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I can't remember a \Ndamn thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.19,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Do you remember the class \Ntrip we took that summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:56.42,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:59.74,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,An accident happened \Nduring it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.88,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Do you remember anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.02,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.97,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Akazawa, the head \Nof countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.33,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:09.47,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Truth be told, \NI don't remember much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:13.69,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I know that someone died \Nup on the mountain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.23,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can't remember either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.52,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I can't even remember \Nwhat kind of accident it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:23.86,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Was the accident before or \Nafter your visit to the shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.08,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Why does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.76,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Well, if it was before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:30.87,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,then perhaps a blessing from \Nthe shrine stopped the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.13,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:38.38,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling that it was a \Nrun-down, abandoned-looking shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.93,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. The shrine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.77,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we went to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.78,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,We all held hands and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.26,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Crap. I can't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:50.69,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Matsunaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.02,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,didn't you leave something \Nbehind, as a clue for the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.19,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,Evidently I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:59.41,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What did you want to tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:05.27,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,All I can remember is having \Nthis urgent need to tell them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You can't remember \Nwhat it was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:12.72,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,And you don't remember \Nwhat you left behind, or where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:15.25,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Like, was it a note, or?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:21.12,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,No... No, it wasn't paper... It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.23,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I think I used something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:29.32,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,That's right! It's at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.47,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I took something to the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.00,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,The school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.74,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Where in the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.44,Default,Nakao,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.12,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,How far out are you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.84,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.13,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.48,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Quit messing around, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.51,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.41,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:14.66,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.66,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I protected them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.76,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,I left it for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.20,Default,Matsunaga,0,0,0,,...in the classroom.
